title: DDFP 227: Super Bowl XLVIII Special, Day 1
itunes:title: DDFP 227: Super Bowl XLVIII Special, Day 1
description:
Shek, Rank, Matt "Money" Smith and Molly Qerim are in New York for Super Bowl XLVIII and are joined by the biggest names in the NFL and entertainment including Maurice Jones-Drew, Michael Irvin, Deion Sanders, actor/ comedian Rob Riggle, Eli Manning and more. Also, follow @NFLcomLIVE -- the official handle for "NFL.com Live: Super Bowl XLVIII."
